		<h2> Find companies that are open to hiring homeless people. </h2>
		
		<div id="users" style="margin-top:20px">
  <input class="search" placeholder="Search" />
  <button class="sort" data-sort="name" style="margin-left:10px">
    Sort by name
  </button>
  
  <ul class="filter" style="margin-top:10px; margin-left:-30px">
  	Filter by:    
    <li class="btn" id="filter-none" style="margin-left:10px">All</li>
    <li class="btn" id="filter-corp">Corporations</li>
    <li class="btn" id="filter-center">Job Centers and Fairs</li>
	</ul>

  <ul class="list">
    <li>
      <h3><a href="http://www.jobs.net/jobs/sfgoodwill/en-us/search/?keyword=&location=San%20Francisco%2C%20Ca" target="_blank"><span class="name">Goodwill</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">Goodwill <span class="category">is</span> known for hiring people who are looking for their first job or their first job in a long time.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="https://www.amazon.jobs/en/locations/san-francisco" target="_blank"><span class="name">Amazon</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">Amazon <span class="category">is</span> known for hiring homeless people for various jobs.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="http://sfgoodwill.org/jobs/non-goodwill-jobs/" target="_blank"><span class="name">CAP Job Center</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">Free and open to all, the Goodwill Comprehensive Access Point (CAP) Job Center offers a wide variety of career navigation 
      services. In the past 12 months, CAP hosted more than 20,000 visits. It’s <span class="category">the</span> best place to begin your search.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="http://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usn/employment-opportunities" target="_blank"><span class="name">Salvation Army</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">Salvation Army <span class="category">is</span> a great resource that not only offers jobs, but also provides many other 
      <a href="http://www.salvationarmyusa.org/usn/plugins/gdosCenterSearch?mode=query_2&lat=37.775&lng=-122.419&code=US&query=san%20francisco"
      target="_blank">services</a> for adults, such as alcohol and drug treatment.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="https://www.thegivingkeys.com/pages/careers" target="_blank"><span class="name">The Giving Keys</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">The Giving Keys <span class="category">is</span> a pay-it-forward fashion company employs those transitioning out of homelessness.
      You can read some <a href="https://www.thegivingkeys.com/pages/employed-for-change" target="_blank">stories</a> of employees at the company.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="http://www.path.org/jobs/" target="_blank"><span class="name">PATH</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">PATH <span class="category">is</span> the leader in global health innovation, and they also hire people who might not have the most experience.</p>
    </li>
     <li>
      <h3><a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/d/ca--san-francisco/career-fair/" target="_blank"><span class="name">San Francisco Career Fairs</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">This resource lists several different career fairs that are happening soon in <span class="category">the</span> San Francisco Bay
      Area. Career Fairs are a great way to learn about several different opportunities and apply for jobs at the same time!</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3><a href="http://www.indeed.com/q-No-Experience-l-San-Francisco,-CA-jobs.html" target="_blank"><span class="name">No Experience Required Jobs</span></a></h3>
      <p class="desc">This resources lists jobs in San Francisco that require no experience. This is
      <span class="category">the</span>  perfect way to get a job to kickstart your career.</p>
    </li>
